# The Plasma appletsrc carries panel layout and applet config worth tracking,
# but KDE writes the *current* wallpaper path into it too -- and the slideshow
# rotates every SlideInterval (30 min here), so the file is otherwise dirty
# permanently and leaks local wallpaper paths into this public repo.
#
# The kde-wallpaper filter strips Image=/SlidePaths= on the way into git only:
# the working copy keeps them, so the live slideshow keeps working. The filter
# is configured per-clone by install.sh (git_settings); a clone that skips it
# just commits the lines again, which is why it lives there and not only here.
os/arch/config/plasma-org.kde.plasma.desktop-appletsrc filter=kde-wallpaper
